channel.desc: The Future Greats are switching it up, evolving their characters, and trying something new. Who will crumble under the added pressure? Sirena Linton shows a more villainous side against Zena, P-Nasty adopts a special finisher in an attempt to take out Tatyanna, and Shiloh Hill goes head-to-head with Elijah Holyfield as both men look to build on their rising momentum.
